Property Owner:  Recreation and Park Department<br>No waiting list&nbsp;<br>Opportunities for gardening available.  This urban farm has no individual plots, but is managed as a collective, with garden beds cared for by a team of volunteers.
Regular workdays are the 1st and 3rd Sundays of the month and the 2nd and 4th Saturdays, Noon to 5 PM. Plus every Monday, 1 PM to 5 PM. At the end of each workday, volunteers get to take produce home.
The Farm also regularly hosts field trips and workshops and sponsors a low-income Community Supported Agriculture (CSA) program. <br><a href='http://www.alemanyfarm.org/' target='_blank'>www.alemanyfarm.org/</a><br>Record last updated 11/20/09&nbsp;
